results.deck: Blitz Games is a developer located in the United Kingdom. Founded by the famous Oliver twins in 1990.
results.description: Blitz Games is an independent game developer based in Leamington Spa in the UK. Founded in 1990 by the twins Andrew and Philip Oliver; the company is broken down into 5 divisions. The various divisions target mature gamers, family friendly titles and simulations for professionals; such as medics in the armed forces.  Some of games they develop feature famous licenses such as Spongebob Squarepants.
